item.title: CVE-2024-1346|2024-08-28T14:57:27.988Z -- laborofficefree -- laborofficefree
item.description: Weak MySQL database root password in LaborOfficeFree affects version 19.10. This vulnerability allows an attacker to calculate the root password of the MySQL database used by LaborOfficeFree using two constants.
